  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E, F, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique functions as Zanmaken, except if a ray is fired, it may pass through any organic matter (including creatures) to reach its intended target, though you suffer a -1 penalty to hit for each creature it passes through. The damage (or bonus damage if used as a melee attack) increases to 4d6 force damage. Using this technique as a melee attack will not increase its perform time.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 1d6 per level or 15d6 damage total, whichever is lower.</p>\n\n",
